The Magento Payment Gateway Plugin for Bitcoin [[API_reference_(JSON-RPC)_RPC_API]] provides the ability for eCommerce sites running Magento to be able to accept bitcoins for payment.

This open source project was released on June 11, 2011 (1.1).

